title: [Caulfield Technical College Annual Review, 1966]
brief_description: An example of student film making. The surfer, riding a child’s tricycle with his surfboard under his arm, enters a park, splashes across an ornamental pond and land-surfs under a sprinkler. No title, no credits available.
